The core AirPlay 2 receiver, RTSP/RAOP stack, HAP pairing and audio pipeline
originate from that project and remain © Rémi Bouteiller. This fork adds:
a redesigned web UI, software audio DSP (tone EQ + 4th-order high-pass,
anti-clipping limiter, output-channel/mono downmix), speaker protection /
amplifier standby, an addressable WS2812 LED-strip effects engine, Home
Assistant MQTT discovery, and a Seeed XIAO ESP32-S3 build target.

